nodes.body: !bench

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/5809a362-2224-4611-8a6f-9ab679d8f43f) for commit 61d9b1c26e5614afe04a2b7416867f72bf3c59be.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/4a928290-0402-48bc-92fb-cb1a91af330b/to/5809a362-2224-4611-8a6f-9ab679d8f43f) against commit 56102518894110f4b30d5d61e3711a9f2c677574:
```diff
  Benchmark                                                Metric         Change
  ==============================================================================
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.SpecialFunctions.Pow.Deriv             instructions   -14.1%
+ ~Mathlib.Analysis.SpecialFunctions.Trigonometric.Deriv   instructions   -17.2%
- ~Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.Matrix.SesquilinearForm           instructions     5.2%
+ ~Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Measure.FiniteMeasure             instructions   -15.0%
+ ~Mathlib.Topology.ContinuousFunction.StoneWeierstrass    instructions   -12.7%
```
@negiizhao The bench results look good. Do you still want to get this merged? If so, could you please resolve conflicts, bench again, and mark this as ready for review?
!bench
I feel it might need a better priority setting, but this PR might be a simple temporary solution (if it is improved). I'll leave the decision to the reviewers.

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/47afb22b-d773-4986-a9bf-7deb6f3f4196) for commit 165cf021e0a4d59e8a2c29397eff0fee24dbc2e4.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/a14b5d75-6b70-4b45-b3da-ad59ecda9b57/to/47afb22b-d773-4986-a9bf-7deb6f3f4196) against commit 17bb4e9a6cf173ab20af2d60ca3e0ec5045f3d9a:
```diff
  Benchmark                                              Metric         Change
  ============================================================================
- ~Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.TensorProduct.Graded.External   instructions    18.9%
+ ~Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Measure.FiniteMeasure           instructions   -13.8%
+ ~Mathlib.Topology.ContinuousFunction.UniqueCFC         instructions    -7.0%
```
!bench
!bench

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/4eb7a81b-d472-486a-9360-99e143baab4a) for commit 3b00df2c963cc62442f0bab236ec12fed871a351.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/a14b5d75-6b70-4b45-b3da-ad59ecda9b57/to/4eb7a81b-d472-486a-9360-99e143baab4a) against commit 17bb4e9a6cf173ab20af2d60ca3e0ec5045f3d9a:
```diff
  Benchmark                                              Metric         Change
  ============================================================================
- ~Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.TensorProduct.Graded.External   instructions    18.8%
+ ~Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Measure.FiniteMeasure           instructions   -13.8%
+ ~Mathlib.Topology.ContinuousFunction.UniqueCFC         instructions    -7.0%
```
!bench

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/1dc6bc20-d4df-4f18-b192-d241179ca396) for commit 039ee4fdafc2638ee3416c4c5fe2bf4414e8cfdd.
The entire run failed.
Found no significant differences.

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/372548e8-f492-4fe5-a610-e5d326416683) for commit e3a757c5b67d437325032c3f372d27607d30f95f.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/a14b5d75-6b70-4b45-b3da-ad59ecda9b57/to/372548e8-f492-4fe5-a610-e5d326416683) against commit 17bb4e9a6cf173ab20af2d60ca3e0ec5045f3d9a:
```diff
  Benchmark                                              Metric         Change
  ============================================================================
- ~Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.TensorProduct.Graded.External   instructions    18.9%
+ ~Mathlib.MeasureTheory.Measure.FiniteMeasure           instructions   -13.8%
+ ~Mathlib.Topology.ContinuousFunction.UniqueCFC         instructions    -7.1%
```
!bench

Here are the [benchmark results](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/run-detail/60be3c36-ceb2-44b8-a49d-427c33f22ad1) for commit 0d03f5b9f86ac1563af8e80a5094ad78d24f39f9.
There were [significant changes](http://speed.lean-fro.org/mathlib4/compare/a14b5d75-6b70-4b45-b3da-ad59ecda9b57/to/60be3c36-ceb2-44b8-a49d-427c33f22ad1) against commit 17bb4e9a6cf173ab20af2d60ca3e0ec5045f3d9a:
```diff
  Benchmark                                             Metric         Change
  ===========================================================================
- ~Mathlib.Analysis.Distribution.SchwartzSpace          instructions    12.1%
- ~Mathlib.Analysis.Fourier.FourierTransformDeriv       instructions    26.5%
- ~Mathlib.Analysis.InnerProductSpace.TwoDim            instructions    15.6%
- ~Mathlib.Analysis.SpecialFunctions.Pow.Deriv          instructions    13.9%
- ~Mathlib.Geometry.Euclidean.Angle.Oriented.Rotation   instructions    16.0%
```
I'm not sure why the improvement is smaller than before, maybe some new instances were added to Mathlib.
